.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH k2i-maintenance-clean-orphans 1  "k2i-maintenance-clean-orphans "
.SH NAME
k2i\-maintenance\-clean\-orphans \- Clean up orphan files
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBk2i\-maintenance\-clean\-orphans\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Clean up orphan files
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.SH EXTRA
BEHAVIOR:
  Compares files present in the warehouse with files referenced by table
  snapshots and deletes orphan files older than orphan_retention_days.
